------------------------------
Installing python-ldap
------------------------------

Prerequisites:

  Required:

    - Python 2.0 or newer (see http://www.python.org)

    - OpenLDAP 2.1.x client libs or newer
      (see http://www.openldap.org)

  Optional:

    - Cyrus SASL 2.1.x or newer (see )

    - OpenSSL 0.9.6 or newer (see http://www.openssl.org)

Quick build instructions:
    edit setup.cfg (see Build/ for platform-specific examples)
    python setup.py build
    python setup.py install

